        {
            "title": "Barclays因歐洲央行鷹派立場及經濟增長放緩而下調歐洲小型股評級",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/73yUHxUfpWvUQL6UbTjBEQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA601YK_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Barclays\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Barclays;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Barclays\">Barclays</a>週二將歐洲小型股評級下調至中性,儘管該類股估值仍具吸引力,但理由是宏觀經濟動能放緩以及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"歐洲央行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:歐洲央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐洲央行\">歐洲央行</a>立場更趨鷹派,根據Barclays研究報告指出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"宏觀經濟動能放緩和歐洲央行加息抑制了近期輪動風險。估值仍具吸引力,但背景尚不足以轉為建設性,\"報告表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐元區即時預測本季已滑入負值區域,2026年GDP增長預測從2024年中的1.6%下滑至約1.1%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ed948697-bef2-36e6-807e-1f8f4977cfa6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德國10年期盈虧平衡通脹率和歐洲央行2026年12月隱含利率自1月以來走高,歐洲央行隱含利率在4月初接近3%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據MSCI和Barclays Research數據,小型股擁擠度在2026年初持續為負,截至4月7日,以兩年百分位數計算接近多年低點。該因子與成長股一樣仍處於低配狀態,但兩者都缺乏近期催化劑,該行表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Bloomberg和Barclays Research數據,截至4月10日,Barclays動態配置模型削減了規模因子敞口,減持成長股和小型股以資助選擇性增持價值股。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Bloomberg和Barclays Research數據,4月季節性因素歷史上為小型股帶來0.5%的相對月度回報,儘管Barclays表示宏觀背景壓過了季節性因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Bloomberg和Barclays Research數據,該因子的成分股與價值股重疊26%,與高波動性股票重疊31%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至4月10日,Barclays歐盟籃子的因子離散度為8.4%,處於第79.4百分位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/barclays%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E9%B7%B9%E6%B4%BE%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E5%8F%8A%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7%E6%94%BE%E7%B7%A9%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E8%82%A1%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-114022659.html",
